      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know man... everything just feels so heavy lately. like i'm just dragging this weight around every single day and there's no point to any of it. my doc keeps bugging me about starting SSRIs or seeing a specialist, but honestly? it feels like they just want to put a band-aid on a gaping wound. like they want to drug me into being a zombie so i don't make a scene. i just feel so tired of fighting a brain that hates me.",
